{"title":"Time, A Friend","date":"2021-07-01T07:30:44.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 1, 2021","L":"07/01/2021","MM-DD":"07-01"},"author":"白桦","link":"2021/07/01/TimeAFriend","comments":true,"tags":["日志","诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2021-07-01T09:49:49.760Z","content":"<iframe allow=\"autoplay *; encrypted-media *; fullscreen *\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"150\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:660px;overflow:hidden;background:transparent;\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-storage-access-by-user-activation allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" src=\"https://embed.music.apple.com/cn/album/the-sounds-of-silence/203925134?i=203925465&l=en\"></iframe>\n<p>雨雾带走清晨<br>\n留下这潮湿、温暖<br>\n且暧昧的空气<br>\n沉重得像是吸了水的棉被</p>\n<p>怕极了日落后<br>\n会变得像钢铁般冰冷</p>\n<p>黄昏未迟<br>\n推开了这雨幕<br>\n无名的风透过<br>\n在暗夜的灯光下</p>\n<p>搭上未至的车<br>\n逐渐轻盈地迈开</p>\n<hr>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/blackCross.webp\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1\">1<a title=\"#1\" href=\"#1\"></a></h3>\n<p>咻——咻——咻——<br>\n不是快门<br>\n这是他们阅读的声音</p>\n<h3 id=\"2\">2<a title=\"#2\" href=\"#2\"></a></h3>\n<p>上帝来救赎灵魂<br>\n灵魂坐在上帝身上<br>\n开心地笑着</p>\n<h3 id=\"3\">3<a title=\"#3\" href=\"#3\"></a></h3>\n<p>长廊下的老太太扇着扇子<br>\n看了我一眼，心里念叨着：<br>\n又是个异乡者</p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p>P.</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"我们灵魂深处感情的需求到底是什么","link":"2021/07/04/ArtificalPartner"},"next":{"title":"Mr.Green","link":"2021/06/11/MrGreen"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2021/07/01/TimeAFriend/","toc":[{"id":"1","title":"1","index":"1"},{"id":"2","title":"2","index":"2"},{"id":"3","title":"3","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"July 1, 2021"},"reading_time":"155 words in 1 min"}